{"tid":1081221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麻疹殺入校園　理大設計學院男宿生中招","createTime":"2019-03-28T07:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T12:25:56.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"32206f451e7e7e380ba322d467be1ab3a298b9b6","tid":1081221,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T07:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190328/photo/bkn-20190328143654920-0328_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190328145010\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190328%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190328143654920-0328_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190328145010&h=affa54ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻疹在機場爆發，更殺入校園！香港理工大學回覆證實，昨日(27日)知悉一名就讀理大設計學院學生染上麻疹，並指患者在醫院接受治療後已康復及出院。 <br />\n<br />\n理大表示，該名學生亦是理大何文田宿舍宿生，校方昨已開始在何文田宿舍相關樓層的公眾地方特別進行消毒，亦有加強大樓其他公眾地方的慣常消毒和清潔安排。據悉，該宗個案為日前公布的其中一名39歲男患者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190328/bkn-20190328143654920-0328_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190328%2Fbkn-20190328143654920-0328_00822_001.html&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7AAoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=024aa07b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190328/bkn-20190328143654920-0328_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"311760be80ea0f51ff1f72bf5890c40a848331f6","tid":1081221,"uid":35014,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T07:07:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24a4291c36b02803e38a7268a70ce69edf8430de","tid":1081221,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"311760be80ea0f51ff1f72bf5890c40a848331f6","tid":1081221,"uid":35014,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T07:07:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T07:10:59.000Z","msg":"真係笑得好7<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2030704/org/cf489e7d3a46c9ee6489225cad05fced.jpg/Vt3EEtks0bffBiuwWdEAVXIF9Ls